Class Astar<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • labyrinth.pathfinding.Astar<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of cell: square, hexagonal, triangular.
    U - Type of labyrinth builder: square, hexagonal, triangular.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Hexastar, Sqastar, Triastar

    public abstract class Astar<T,U>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the abstract class of the A* algorithm. In contains the code required to implement the pathfinding.

    Daniel Castaño Estrella
